bination of regulation and temperament and bad memories there is just less =
of this sort of thing in traditional finance. Still lots! But=C2=A0less of =
it,=C2=A0more constrained, less leveraged. Everyone in traditional finance =
has seen this movie before and knows how it ends.=C2=A0And yet there is som=
e =E2=80=A6=C2=A0natural =E2=80=A6=C2=A0human =E2=80=A6=C2=A0longing =E2=80=
=A6 to borrow short and lend long with no equity? I dunno. Since 2008, the =
