5px;">Archegos</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bill Hwang is a former hedge fund mana=
ger who most recently invested his own money through a family office that h=
e called Archegos Capital Management. Archegos <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28218867.272582/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
NvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDQtMDUvYmlsbC1od2FuZy1zLWFyY2hlZ29zLXN3Y=
XAtYWZ0ZXJtYXRoLWlzLWF3a3dhcmQtZm9yLWJhbmtzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA2MjkyMl9NT05FWVNU=
